---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { SITE_CONFIG } from '../../config.js';
---

<MainLayout 
  title="Stump Grinding & Removal Florida | Clear Your Lawn" 
  description="Professional stump grinding services to eliminate trip hazards and pests. Reclaim your Florida backyard today."
>
  <header style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2d6a4f 0%, #1b4332 100%); color: white; padding: 6rem 1rem; text-align: center;">
    <h1 style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4rem); margin: 0; font-weight: 900;">Stump Grinding</h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #95d5b2; margin-top: 1rem;">Complete removal of underground hazards and eyesores.</p>
  </header>

  <main class="container" style="max-width: 900px; padding-top: 5rem; padding-bottom: 12rem;">
    <div style="line-height: 1.9; color: #374151; font-size: 1.2rem;">
        <h2 style="color: #064e3b; font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800;">Don't Leave the Stump Behind</h2>
        <p>A cut tree is only half the job. Leftover stumps are trip hazards, lawnmower killers, and most importantly in Florida, <strong>magnets for termites</strong> and wood-boring pests. Our crews use high-powered machinery to grind stumps well below the surface.</p>
        
        <h3 style="color: #064e3b; margin-top: 3rem;">Why Grind the Stump?</h3>
        <ul style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
            <li><strong>Pest Prevention:</strong> Eliminates nesting grounds for termites and ants.</li>
            <li><strong>Safety:</strong> Removes hidden trip hazards for families and pets.</li>
            <li><strong>Replanting:</strong> Prepares the ground for new sod or trees.</li>
            <li><strong>Aesthetics:</strong> Provides a clean, flat finish to your landscape.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 5rem;">
        <a href={SITE_CONFIG.phoneHref} style="background: #ea580c; color: white !important; padding: 1.5rem 3rem; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 16px; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.5rem; display: inline-block;">
            GET A STUMP QUOTE
        </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</MainLayout>